-- Citic May Raise 80 Billion Yuan in Hong Kong Initial Offering, Daily Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-21T22:50:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/citic-may-raise-80-billion-yuan-in-hong-kong-initial-offering-daily-says.html

          
          
             Citic Group may raise as much as 80
billion yuan in a planned initial public offering in Hong Kong,
the China Daily reported, citing unidentified people familiar
with the matter.  
 Citic Group aims to list by the end of next year, the
report said.  
 The Beijing-based company currently has listed units Citic
Pacific Ltd., China CITIC Bank Corp. and CITIC
Securities Co.  
          
          


  


        